I patiently reviewed again the situation I reported and found that it's not a bug of _django-json-api_. To get what I wanted I used the functionalities of this project, as well as a small customization.

There was a mistake in the sample code I had, because the User object I used for testing did not have its corresponding UserProfile object, being this the reason for not having the "_relationships_" part in in the generated JSON output.

I was very fortunate because someone very gently at the _#rest_framework_ IRC channel helped me to analyse the situation, providing me a [detailed good working and simple sample, which is available as a Gist](https://gist.github.com/freakabcd/9ec94d4fb9e285bc73d328a8a78cedba). The most interesting part of that sample output is this:

